<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَقَالَ الَّذِي نَجَا مِنْهُمَا وَادَّكَرَ بَعْدَ أُمَّةٍ أَنَا أُنَبِّئُكُمْ بِتَأوِيلِهِ فَأَرْسِلُونِ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٩ص٣٢:</span> <span class="c3">{وَادَّكَرَ}</span>: افْتَعَلَ مِنْ ذَكَرَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{أُمَّةٍ}</span>: قَرْنٍ،<span class="c5"> وَتُقْرَأُ:</span> أَمَهٍ: نِسْيَانٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [يوسف: ٤٥]</p> </div>